1. *Vašington* je glavni grad Sjedinjenih Američkih Država. (Washington is the capital city of the United States of America.)
2. Ukoliko želite da posetite *Vašington*, trebalo bi da se informišete o viznom režimu. (If you want to visit Washington, you should inform yourself about the visa regime.)
3. Kongres Sjedinjenih Američkih Država se nalazi u *Vašingtonu*. (The United States Congress is located in Washington.)
4. *Vašingtonski* sporazum je doveo do značajnih promena u međunarodnoj politici. (The Washington Agreement has led to significant changes in international politics.)
5. *Vašingtona* ima mnogo znamenitosti koje turisti obično posećuju. (Washington has many landmarks that tourists usually visit.)
6. *Vašingtonov* govor je bio inspirativan i uticao je na mnoge ljude širom sveta. (Washington's speech was inspirational and had an impact on many people around the world.)
7. *Vašingtonski* konsenzus se smatra važnim ekonomskim dokumentom. (The Washington Consensus is considered an important economic document.)
8. Nacionalni muzej američke istorije se nalazi u *Vašingtonu*. (The National Museum of American History is located in Washington.)
9. *Vašingtonov* spomenik se nalazi u središtu grada. (The Washington Monument is located in the center of the city.)
10. Predsednička palata u *Vašingtonu* se naziva Bela kuća. (The presidential palace in Washington is called the White House.)